From 94d187acd56164ec751cc12de113c16976ce3408 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Carlos Garnacho <carlosg@gnome.org>
Date: Sun, 23 Nov 2025 16:10:08 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] libmediaart: Add glycin based implementation

With gdk-pixbuf being sunset, it makes sense to add a Glycin-based
implementation to extract media art. This new implementation will
take precedence if both gdk-pixbuf and glycin are found.
---
 libmediaart/extractglycin.c | 185 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 libmediaart/meson.build     |   2 +
 meson.build                 |  10 ++
 meson_options.txt           |   2 +-
 4 files changed, 198 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)
 create mode 100644 libmediaart/extractglycin.c

diff --git a/libmediaart/extractglycin.c b/libmediaart/extractglycin.c
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..3a394b6
--- /dev/null
+++ b/libmediaart/extractglycin.c
@@ -0,0 +1,185 @@
+/*
+ * Copyright (C) 2025, Carlos Garnacho
+ *
